question: What are Dr. Sharada U Shenoy's educational qualifications past experience?

question: What is the main objective of Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning program, and what role does the Centre of Excellence in AI and ML play in achieving this objective?

answer: The main objective of offering the Bachelor of Technology in Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning program is to develop skilled professionals in the field of AI & ML. The Centre of Excellence in AI and ML supports this objective by providing the latest computers, amenities, and resources for research work, projects, and regular curricular activities for students and research scholars. For more details, you can visit [this link](https://nmamit.nitte.edu.in/department-AI&ML.php#Overview).
